{"tid":1973667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[泰國戰線] 支那人食酒店自助餐搶蝦， 醜態百出","createTime":"2020-04-15T10:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T10:49:46.000Z","uid":30743,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c644f57b1939c77d2ef5d840bac1653476ee0b","tid":1973667,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:15:36.000Z","msg":"社交網昨日起瘋傳一段影片，顯示一批操普通話的遊客在泰國清邁一間酒店享用自助餐時，毫無儀態地用碟子瘋狂鏟蝦，一次過拿着數盤「戰利品」返回座位，盡顯「唔執輸」心態，但事後卻吃剩不少蝦及其他食物。有留言者指涉事旅客是內地人，內地有網民亦和應，狠批個別同胞出遊時的行為令中國丟架，且是浪費食物。有泰國網民則留言嘲諷：「生下來到現在都沒吃過蝦嗎？」亦有網民指搶蝦情況有如「餓鬼爭食」，更稱人比餓鬼更恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20160319/s00004/1458376088680SL4_30E8AED9BB92184362D13C8276A4FDF9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20160319%2Fs00004%2F1458376088680SL4_30E8AED9BB92184362D13C8276A4FDF9.jpg&h=c747379c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該片段由泰國網指上傳至facebook，指事發現場為當地龍頭免稅店企業皇權（King Power）的自助餐廳內，聲稱一批相信是中國遊客一踴而上，在放滿蝦的冰池邊，未有使用夾子或勺子，反而是直接地「手起碟落」，如在戰場般大動作瘋狂撈蝦，不少人滿載而歸，捧着2至3盤滿滿的蝦子回座位。<br />\n<br />\n然而，從另一批照片可見，遊客在用餐後桌面一片狼藉，多張餐桌上均有大量吃剩的食物，當中包括一盤盤的蝦子，非常浪費。<br />\n<br />\n有內地網民指相信該批是中國客，批評有關行為是「丟盡國人的臉」，又稱「下次泰國人見到中國人應該會說：中國是不是沒蝦！」。有人則認為，問題不僅在於秩序混亂，而是造成浪費。另有人慨嘆，出國的人大都有些經濟能力，質疑為何要為搶食至如此瘋狂。<br />\n<br />\n事件在網上瘋傳後，在台灣以至英國多間傳媒均有報道，網民形容「中國遊客舉動又再揚威國際」。<br />\n<br />\n（星暹傳媒、微博）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20160319/s00004/1458376655741/%e3%80%90%e7%9f%ad%e7%89%87-%e5%a4%9a%e5%9c%96%e3%80%91%e7%96%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%97%85%e5%ae%a2%e6%b3%b0%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ab%e8%87%aa%e5%8a%a9%e9%a4%90-%e7%94%a8%e7%a2%9f%e7%98%8b%e7%8b%82%e6%90%b6%e8%9d%a6-%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91-%e9%a4%93%e9%ac%bc%e7%88%ad%e9%a3%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20160319%2Fs00004%2F1458376655741%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%259f%25ad%25e7%2589%2587-%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%259c%2596%25e3%2580%2591%25e7%2596%2591%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%2597%2585%25e5%25ae%25a2%25e6%25b3%25b0%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ab%25e8%2587%25aa%25e5%258a%25a9%25e9%25a4%2590-%25e7%2594%25a8%25e7%25a2%259f%25e7%2598%258b%25e7%258b%2582%25e6%2590%25b6%25e8%259d%25a6-%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e6%25b0%2591-%25e9%25a4%2593%25e9%25ac%25bc%25e7%2588%25ad%25e9%25a3%259f&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQNAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=f3da6f30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20160319%2Fs00004%2F1458376655741%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%259f%25ad%25e7%2589%2587-%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%259c%2596%25e3%2580%2591%25e7%2596%2591%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%2597%2585%25e5%25ae%25a2%25e6%25b3%25b0%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ab%25e8%2587%25aa%25e5%258a%25a9%25e9%25a4%2590-%25e7%2594%25a8%25e7%25a2%259f%25e7%2598%258b%25e7%258b%2582%25e6%2590%25b6%25e8%259d%25a6-%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e6%25b0%2591-%25e9%25a4%2593%25e9%25ac%25bc%25e7%2588%25ad%25e9%25a3%259f&h=c585d1f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20160319/s00004/1458376655741/%e3%80%90%e7%9f%ad%e7%89%87-%e5%a4%9a%e5%9c%96%e3%80%91%e7%96%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%97%85%e5%ae%a2%e6%b3%b0%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ab%e8%87%aa%e5%8a%a9%e9%a4%90-%e7%94%a8%e7%a2%9f%e7%98%8b%e7%8b%82%e6%90%b6%e8%9d%a6-%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91-%e9%a4%93%e9%ac%bc%e7%88%ad%e9%a3%9f</a>"},{"pid":"b103acaf7aeaded5177de616029ae7fc357c38e1","tid":1973667,"uid":30743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/is4UCUzjNgY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fis4UCUzjNgY&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQNAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=fd07bd99\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/is4UCUzjNgY</a>"},{"pid":"7ce8f16724e99f79a1b6a0bc5c9504f6aab9cb32","tid":1973667,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"食咁多會痛風"},{"pid":"35232ead68927891d59322a858ec4626009cdc23","tid":1973667,"